message: Guys um trying to go for a four letters .me domain the problem is there is a .com domain is taken .. What do you think when it come to SEO and branding Thanks in advance.. People similar with experience will be highly appreciated to answer

data.message: Mahmoud Hisham Maged Atef Pls advise ya w7oosh el SEO?

Google didn't announce anything about TLDs except once, saying that they will rank .edu domains better in search results related to questions.
So nothing special to say. but you should think in a different way. from user experience point of view, will you trust clicking a .me website more than a .com website? most people don't
I also have a personal concern regarding the .me TLD; the .me is a ccTLD to Montenegro, which is misleading to search engines, they may rank you lower in Local egyptian searches as they believe you are targeting another country. You can just search with ".me domain meaning" to find that Google gives you as the best answer " it's a ccTLD to Montenegro"
I recommend going with the .com with another domain name or at least choosing another global TLD.
Technically there is absolutely no difference which domain extension you wanna use for SEO. But for branding when somebody seeks a site, the *.com is always primary. Ahmed Salah Mahmoud Mostafa
